[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "――そういうわけで、ユリエさんが\n『ランターナ紀行』を書くことになったのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……そう。姉さん、あの話を受けたのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "それで、見たこと聞いたことを本にするためにも、\nこの広大なランターナ王国中を巡るんですって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……ふうん。\n姉さん、また落ち着かないわけね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "そういう言い方はないんじゃない？　\nまあ、確かにじっとしていられない性分ではあるけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……私も、姉さんの旅についていくわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "あら、珍しい。\nあなたも何か目的があるの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "うん。ちょっと、やりたいことがある",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "旅に同行すれば色々な場所を回れるだろうから、\n欲しい素材も採取できそうだし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "そうね。それなら、いい選択だと思うわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "話は聞こえていたわ。\nミルカ、あなたも来るのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……うん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そう、分かったわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "二人とも、気を付けて行ってきて。\nユリエさん、紀行文の完成、楽しみにしてるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ありがとう、マリオン。\n必ずいいものにするわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ミルカ。旅の途中、\n何か困ったことがあれば、すぐに言いなさい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……分かってる。\n姉さんも無理はしないで",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ、約束する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "あなたがいてくれるなら、\nどんな困難も乗り越えられる気がする",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……そう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "それにしても珍しい。\nミルカが一緒に行きたいだなんて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "別に",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "それじゃあ、二人とも。いい旅を",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "うん、行ってくる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "マリオン・クィン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion Quin",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "異邦人の女性。真面目な仕事人間。\nレスナたちからアトリエの管理を任されている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ・クロッツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca Crotze",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "もの静かな錬金術士。ユリエの妹。\n素直ゆえに発言が辛辣になってしまいがち",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]